        Reading Buyer Signals at Your Open Home in Brisbane
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        What agents watch for at open homes, how to interpret buyer feedback, and what silence actually means versus genuine interest.
      </p>
